{"tid":2456173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 吳保錡(poki)奇遇記分享","createTime":"2021-03-21T16:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T22:07:09.000Z","uid":382981,"like":72,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"329683a388c9673bc3fc0cea54b10bf6b1c9b0da","tid":2456173,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，件事大概係4個月前左右，由於我冇睇viu台嘅關係，事前喺真喺我唔識香港嘅viu台明星。<br />\n<br />\n小弟是做酒店reception嘅，有一日，poki出現喺大堂個lobby，而我就喺唯一一個企緊counter，佢就行埋嚟問我嘢，我重申一次，我嗰刻真的不知道吳保錡是誰。<br />\n<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npoki <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有咩可以幫到你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有冇得睇下你哋個ball房<br />\n心諗乜撚嘢ball房呀屌你老母，冇受過教育？<br />\nBallroom就Ballroom啦，我記得嗰時係夜晚9點幾同個ballroom有event做緊，佢嗰樣仲要好撚臭寸<br />\n再加上睇ballroom喺要搵event sales預約時間先可以睇，唔撚喺話睇就睇，你估你喺大明星？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔好意思先生，我哋而家個ballroom有event進行緊，如果要睇嘅話(比咗張酒店卡片佢)，可以同我哋event sales預約返個時間呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下？你哋而家冇sell屎咩？<br />\n屌你，9點幾收撚哂工啦，嗰腦裝屎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 𠵱嗰時間都多數已經收哂工架啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哈，咁準時呀，咁你叫你經理出來，你幫唔到我。<br />\n嗰一刻已經好想打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好呀，請問先生貴姓呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我喎！(佢指著自己個樣)<br />\n心諗who the fuck are you? 我再問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 先生貴姓？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你叫你經理出嚟啦，你經理會識得我。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 請你等等。<br />\n<br />\n最正喺。。。我經理。。。唔識講廣東話，黑人嚟，亦都冇睇過viu台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Good evening sir, how may I help you?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Er... I want see ballroom.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : I am very sorry that there&rsquo;s an event on going in the ballroom which is quite impossible to show you. But you may contact our event sales associate for any further questions. (又比張酒店卡片佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thank you<br />\n佢望一望經理，望一望張卡片，再望一望我，之後就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後經理問我佢邊位，我話我都唔識佢，之後我都係問同事先知道佢原來喺poki。"},{"pid":"d1d53bc56fdfd8467f6e84f46db03b61364dd77d","tid":2456173,"uid":157074,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"好柒<br />\n句:我喎<br />\n暗星扮明星"},{"pid":"123a5b915c40f5250e0c3fe53895ae6738a3798e","tid":2456173,"uid":61766,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"同班狗一樣，一見到對方係講英文就笠水"},{"pid":"82812f4a922d9f4cadf1368a2f1eb6e3b98865c6","tid":2456173,"uid":157074,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"唔講以為係八兩金"},{"pid":"1752e7a7c5ab0e5ac94a0779d5814b12e2c60de6","tid":2456173,"uid":109136,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"唯萎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4888bb109b0665c219321361167b0b8ec688d711","tid":2456173,"uid":2419,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇真心"},{"pid":"c54db1569e8054070198366d7948f7c40e1e84db","tid":2456173,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"佢個死款都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7096d4a394a45270d3201cab8759857ba1d7e5","tid":2456173,"uid":30274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4888bb109b0665c219321361167b0b8ec688d711","tid":2456173,"uid":2419,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇真心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"樓上已經有幾隻"},{"pid":"e00f75ccc8cbb1b9aa74fff73c661de40dac1e54","tid":2456173,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4888bb109b0665c219321361167b0b8ec688d711","tid":2456173,"uid":2419,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇真心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老濛"},{"pid":"5313d3b4e3f5392bc98e19328c7df769306366ba","tid":2456173,"uid":47768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"好多真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20d509cd59296f00c37e80b940dac95c12ae2b1","tid":2456173,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"我喎"},{"pid":"761e99ffa71fe66c868cfe38ba3cb9cf299b3658","tid":2456173,"uid":11607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"睇到ball房就笑咗出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181dfb3a11a931a0ef441b24f90bd5f629c8f8da","tid":2456173,"uid":102589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"篇文好熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d539413998702bfd51a076b293037f2bc9b9c76","tid":2456173,"uid":247636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"其實原文出自邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b0d77b910aa2337f7014bd096ac738f39ba136","tid":2456173,"uid":382981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d539413998702bfd51a076b293037f2bc9b9c76","tid":2456173,"uid":247636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"其實原文出自邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"出自用戶，練美欺 (我)"},{"pid":"9d1b02dd4ad32c3777767c4c23533913b94ef761","tid":2456173,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"講埋個名 我都係唔識"},{"pid":"6d7cb362b96fa96073f6642e147a575c1c334107","tid":2456173,"uid":124573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"poke 我就識<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AEVvb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AEVvb4.jpg&h=b3f28fc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"872450db088dfc7736f5c69fc095518a7aff2bc4","tid":2456173,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"我家姐一路都在太古廣場一間名牌做sales<br />\n間店有好多有錢人同名人幫襯<br />\n做了很多年，已經是senior<br />\n咁多年黎都好俾心機做，經理亦好like佢<br />\n因為收入不錯又隱定，家姐原本諗住同拍拖多年既bf結婚<br />\n<br />\n咁多年黎我家姐好少俾人投訴<br />\n而且同好多大客既關係都唔錯<br />\n前排關心研去過我家姐間店幫襯<br />\n不過serve佢既不是我家姐，但佢一買就買左好多野<br />\n<br />\n過左個幾星期，佢又再去間店行<br />\n上次serve果個Day-off, 咁我家姐就頂上serve佢<br />\n開頭已經好有禮貌介紹d新貨俾佢, 仲話俾折頭佢<br />\n佢就無乜反應，望一望另一堆客<br />\n果堆客係大陸人，三至四個，講野好大聲<br />\n關小姐就同我家姐講話可唔可以關左間鋪一陣<br />\n等佢揀衫<br />\n我家姐同我講，佢公司一向唔俾佢地咁做<br />\n驚做壞個頭，除非真係有乜大人物，好多記者好混亂先可以咁做<br />\n但佢見到關小姐黑口黑面，都識做話打電話去問一問老闆<br />\n老闆梗係話唔得啦，至多俾多d折頭她<br />\n<br />\n咁關小姐就發老脾，鬧到我家姐一面屁<br />\nd說話勁難聽，又話自己買野既錢多過我家姐搵幾年既錢<br />\n我家姐都唔敢得罪佢，一味道歉<br />\n<br />\n跟住關小姐就走左人，家姐就同老闆備案<br />\n老闆了解左情況就無再追問<br />\n<br />\n過左兩日佢接到老闆電話話收到complaint<br />\n話有人投訴佢態度唔好，唔理顧客感受<br />\n公司policy一向唔話俾佢地知係邊次事件<br />\n我家姐估黎估去都淨係得失過關小姐一人<br />\n總之俾老闊話左兩句<br />\n<br />\n又過幾日，關小姐又黎<br />\n這次和件西裝友一齊，但好在成店都無其他客<br />\n我家姐怕又惹事，叫左個junior過去serve佢<br />\n點知條老西友係要點番我家姐serve..<br />\n<br />\n根住關小姐就玩野，試衫，但話d衫俾其他人試過污糟<br />\n要開新衫試，我家姐雖然知公司唔俾咁做，<br />\n但怕左佢，唯有照做<br />\n點知試左兩三件，件件佢都要咁試又無話要<br />\n我家姐終於話唔好意思，其實唔可以咁做<br />\n(根本明知她玩野啦.....)<br />\n又係至多俾多d折頭佢<br />\n跟住佢件西裝友就鬧我定姐話&quot;係咪話我地無錢買你地d野?&quot;<br />\n我家姐話唔係，但佢照鬧<br />\n鬧左十幾分鐘<br />\nd同事見咁幫手，又照鬧<br />\n最終打俾老闆備案<br />\n<br />\n之後連收兩封warning letter<br />\n早兩日接埋大信封<br />\n年尾俾人炒左"},{"pid":"ce46dbbef0a497243da2e84a63f0ae5353015723","tid":2456173,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚柒"},{"pid":"7ea4f9f24e0e8b21ed374fdbb9cb4ccde056f7b1","tid":2456173,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"叫經理嗰下已經知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c3b758f3e9a522a1a2a434113511e244553134","tid":2456173,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔止個樣 連個格都同八兩金真人一樣咁衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6dfc6681e64e47da6c438590ccbf3e8624804","tid":2456173,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"連八両金 樓主都認唔出<br />\n樓主一定唔識八両金"},{"pid":"1d1be768444cdb33aa6453c912900b80ee10a501","tid":2456173,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"好撚老實，我都係最近先真係算認得姜濤<br />\nmirror其他人完全唔識<br />\n<br />\n拍打天下果個，見到應該有少少印像，不過唔知咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nerror真係只認得以前跟遊學修搵食果個劉華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但全名係咩都唔知"},{"pid":"6d43af92c90a93314f00db9aa128f16b38e97177","tid":2456173,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T22:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}